# MCP Workspace Isolation Rule

When operating within the FleetMan workspace, you MUST strictly use the following project identifiers when interacting with any Model Context Protocol (MCP) servers (Vercel, Supabase). You are expressly forbidden from listing, reading, or deploying to any other projects.

## Vercel MCP
- **Project ID**: `prj_YEBtNxsQHaXCUoOAdJP0YTJwNXzf`
- **Team ID**: `team_QvCmtB39fQmCmLF41XnzP5de`

